OL,7,FLast February Robinson, from Castle
OL,8,FRise in Tandragee, entered a guilty
OL,9,Fplea to the single charge against him
OL,10,Fof fraud by abusing his position of
OL,11,Ftrust within the Almac Group in that
OL,12,Fbetween 1 January 2020 and 26 May 2022
OL,13,F"whilst occupying a position in which
OL,14,Fyou were expected to safeguard or not
OL,15,Fto act against the financial interests
OL,16,Fof Almac Group, dishonestly abused
OL,17,Fthat position in that you ordered
OL,18,Fgoods on behalf of Alamac Group and
OL,19,Fappropriated them for your own use or
OL,20,Fdisposal, with the intention, by means
OL,21,Fof the abuse of that position to make
OL,22,Fa gain for yourself."
